Wedge.create(manufacturer: "Taylormade", model: "Milled Grind Wedge", loft: "46.0, 48.0, 52.0, 54.0, 56.0, 58.0, 60.0, 62.0", description: "The precision and control of Milled Grind (MG) wedges is now available in a new black finish. The MG Black wedge’s new color presents a darker, solid look at address, adding an aggressive styling to a wedge that already features precision milling, perfectly crafted grinds, and ZTP grooves for maximum spin.

